title: Russo in for PA #92Noon!
description: Michael Russo fills in for PA from the X for a Minnesota Wild heavy show! Features Anthony Lapanta for the first hour, Lavelle on baseball on late arrivals in the middle, and Pat Micheletti for the 11am stretch. Winnipeg Jets writer Ken Wiebe also offers insight into a potential Wild playoff opponent.
